Plot: As a housewife prepares her husband's surprise 50th birthday party, a low-level smuggler is left stranded in the Mexican desert by the Cartel. When the husband arrives at the party, the surprise is not what anyone expects.
Title: One Last Run
Writer: Jeff Brody, Nick Herrera, Carolyn Hoffmann, Robert Lopez
Actors: Jeff Brody, Nicole Erwin, Nick Herrera, Carolyn Hoffmann
